{"tid":117213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5遊台港人住公寓 關窗洗澡一氧化碳中毒","createTime":"2017-02-12T04:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T23:16:39.000Z","uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af4170476b06a92d237c1edabe41226c618d36bd","tid":117213,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170212&amp;guid=56293280&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170212%26guid%3D56293280%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=57e2fe3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170212%26guid%3D56293280%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=ea6e58ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170212&amp;guid=56293280&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n農曆新年後的低溫寒流來襲，台北市接連發生一氧化碳中毒事件，今天凌晨大安區和平東路三段，5名香港遊客疑關窗洗澡，一氧化碳中毒需要送院。<br />\n<br />\n事發凌晨1時許，消防隊獲報到場後，發現屋內5名香港籍遊客，也因為門窗緊閉，開熱水器洗澡，導致一氧化碳在室內大量積聚，趕緊開窗通風，並將4女1男，年約25歲的5人引導下樓，並送上救護車，消防偵測屋內一氧化碳數值為40ppm，發現熱水器裝設於室內，並緊閉門窗洗澡導致通風不良，目前5人因身體不適，送往醫院救護，均無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n差不多同一時間，另外有4新加坡、1名大陸遊客，亦因為一氧化炭中毒，要送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n台北市消防局呼籲民眾，天冷家中更要多注意通風，家中可安裝強制排氣熱水器，還有多注意熱水器安裝位置，家中如果有使用暖爐也要注意通風，避免因為通風不良導致一氧化碳中毒，如在家中有身體不適，請立即打119求救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4N70z1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4N70z1.jpg&h=fb588086&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fca440c144e4bd719e69c454e3e27a3498d63293","tid":117213,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"4女1男"},{"pid":"0494c0fac2015e3670397770264bd46b614c9842","tid":117213,"uid":23973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4女1男</blockquote><br />\n幸福賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71d83954ba50a5478fcad1388d970656754f516","tid":117213,"uid":23914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"台灣d設備會唔會太舊 燃燒時居然冇抽到室外"},{"pid":"0103e607bd8c0370e340b8378e59558321472392","tid":117213,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4女1男</blockquote><br />\n幸福賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d好明顯係比人點去做呀四架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8d4d50cad51486feb07420cf48fd95aaf538ea","tid":117213,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"十年前同2名女同事及佢地二名朋友去大陸玩，屈蛇住酒店，佢地睡床我地下。<br />\n<br />\n初頭佢地換衫都叫我去廁所先，但最後幾天只叫我轉身，其實個feel幾正"},{"pid":"e74c43956be1367729c456b497659fdbeca160af","tid":117213,"uid":5015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十年前同2名女同事及佢地二名朋友去大陸玩，屈蛇住酒店，佢地睡床我地下。<br />\n<br />\n初頭佢地換衫都叫我去廁所先，但最後幾天只叫我轉身，其實個feel幾正</blockquote><br />\n有係偷睇先 btw 你靚仔？"},{"pid":"e1e3f6273fc3842b9c58731a9cc11da0f901b532","tid":117213,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">香港籍遊客</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485cc0416e0fe4c82e4d7a6540ef04e5256ed096","tid":117213,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十年前同2名女同事及佢地二名朋友去大陸玩，屈蛇住酒店，佢地睡床我地下。<br />\n<br />\n初頭佢地換衫都叫我去廁所先，但最後幾